495111338\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image2017-4-4 8:54:6.png\" data-base-url=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"495111419\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" /></span></li>\r\n 	<li>Right click over this icon and select \"Show Manager\".\r\nThe following windows will appear :\r\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" src=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com/download/attachments/495111419/image2017-4-4%2016%3A35%3A19.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1491316520000&amp;api=v2\" height=\"250\" data-image-src=\"/download/attachments/495111419/image2017-4-4%2016%3A35%3A19.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1491316520000&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"495115886\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image2017-4-4 16:35:19.png\" data-base-url=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"495111419\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" /></span></li>\r\n 	<li>Click on \"+ Add\" to create a new Drive.\r\nThe following windows will appear :\r\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" src=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com/download/attachments/495111419/image2017-4-4%2016%3A39%3A26.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1491316767000&amp;api=v2\" height=\"250\" data-image-src=\"/download/attachments/495111419/image2017-4-4%2016%3A39%3A26.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1491316767000&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"495115909\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image2017-4-4 16:39:26.png\" data-base-url=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"495111419\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" /></span>\r\nFill the values :\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Drive Name : it is an alias just for you</li>\r\n 	<li>Host : the machine that you expect to reach</li>\r\n 	<li>Username : the login name on the Host</li>\r\n 	<li>Authentication method : select \"PrivateKey\"</li>\r\n 	<li>PrivateKey : provide the location of the one that you have already generated using puttygen\r\n(If needed, indicate you PassPhrase just below)</li>\r\n 	<li>Directory : the remote location on the Host</li>\r\n 	<li>Drive letter : the windows Drive that will be used</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Click over the \"Save\" button.\r\nThe following windows will appear :\r\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" src=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com/download/attachments/495111419/image2017-4-4%2016%3A46%3A13.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1491317173000&amp;api=v2\" height=\"250\" data-image-src=\"/download/attachments/495111419/image2017-4-4%2016%3A46%3A13.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1491317173000&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"495115943\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image2017-4-4 16:46:13.png\" data-base-url=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"495111419\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" /></span>\r\nThe \"Drive name\" is now listed in the known configurations.</li>\r\n 	<li>Click over the \"Mount\" button.\r\nThe following windows will appear :\r\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" src=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com/download/attachments/495111419/image2017-4-4%2017%3A34%3A18.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1491320058000&amp;api=v2\" height=\"250\" data-image-src=\"/download/attachments/495111419/image2017-4-4%2017%3A34%3A18.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1491320058000&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"495116210\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image2017-4-4 17:34:18.png\" data-base-url=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"495111419\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" /></span>\r\nThe \"Mount\" button has been changed to \"Unmount\" and a new drive has appeared in the File Browser :\r\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" src=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com/download/attachments/495111419/image2017-4-4%2017%3A33%3A43.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1491320024000&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"/download/attachments/495111419/image2017-4-4%2017%3A33%3A43.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1491320024000&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"495116207\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image2017-4-4 17:33:43.png\" data-base-url=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"495111419\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" /></span></li>\r\n 	<li></li>\r\n</ol>','How to install sshfs','','publish','open','open','','how-to-install-sshfs','','','2019-05-06 02:21:31','2019-05-06 02:21:31','',0,'http://45.77.202.181/?p=181',0,'post','',0),(186,1,'2018-10-19 02:24:36','2018-10-19 02:24:36','<h